<p><strong>About Global</strong></p>

<p>Global is one of the world's leading Media &amp; Entertainment groups. It is Europe's largest radio company and one of the leading Outdoor companies in both the UK &amp; Europe. Global is home to respected, national, market leading media brands including Capital, Heart, Classic FM, LBC, Global's Newsroom, Smooth, Radio X, Capital XTRA, Gold and Global Player, which allows listeners to enjoy all of Global's radio brands, award-winning podcasts, and expertly-curated playlists, in one place in app, on web and on smart speakers.</p>

